# {{appName}}

Scaffolded with [Risotron Studio](https://github.com/risotron/risotron).

## Prerequisites (Machine A — dev)
- Node 20+, corepack (`corepack enable`)
- [gh CLI](https://cli.github.com/) authenticated: `gh auth login`

## Install
    pnpm install   # or npm install

## Develop
    pnpm start     # electron-forge start — live reload via Vite

## Publish a new version
1. `npm version patch|minor|major` — bumps version, commits, tags
2. `risotron publish` — builds, ad-hoc signs, uploads DMG + zip to release repo

## Install on another Mac (Machine B)
1. Download the DMG from the release repo
2. Open the DMG and drag `{{appName}}.app` to `/Applications`
3. First launch is blocked by Gatekeeper. Run ONCE in Terminal:

       xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine /Applications/{{appName}}.app

4. Launch the app normally.
5. Click **Check for Updates** → **Update** to pull subsequent versions.
